values.value: MEMBER: THANK YOU FOR USING A NETWORK PROVIDER FOR THESE SERVICES. IF YOU ARE BILLED BY THIS PROVIDER FOR ANY AMOUNTS EXCEEDING YOUR APPLICABLE DEDUCTIBLE, COINSURANCE AND/OR COPAYMENT, PLEASE CONTACT CUSTOMER SERVICES AT THE TOLL-FREE NUMBER ON THE BACK OF YOUR ID CARD.
